ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAuthority for the transfer to WILDLIFE HABITAT CANADA, a non-profit organization, of Crown property consisting of Wildlife Habitat Conservation Stamps, including booklets, corner blocks and panes thereof, in accordance with a three-year Agreement allowing them to use the stamp to raise funds for conservation initiatives in Canada, on a royalty-free basis.
